                   <div style=\"height: 8px; width: 100%; background: #dbe4ef; border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden;\">\n                        <div style=\"height: 100%; width: 37%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f699, #3b82f6); border-radius: 99px;\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            \n                <div style=\"padding: 12px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #e6edf5;\">\n                    <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #1f2937; font-weight: 700;\">\n                        <span>transaction.page.view</span>\n                        <span style=\"color: #3b82f6; font-weight: 800;\">58%</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div style=\"height: 8px; width: 100%; background: #dbe4ef; border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden;\">\n                        <div style=\"height: 100%; width: 58%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f699, #3b82f6); border-radius: 99px;\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div></section>\n\n        <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 18px; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #dbe5f1; box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.05); line-height: 1.3;\">\n            <h4 style=\"margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;\">\n                <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 4px; height: 16px; background: #10b981; border-radius: 2px;\"></span>\n                Global Footprint (Continent-wise Traffic)\n            </h4>\n            <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;\">\n        \n                <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(120px, 160px) 1fr 60px 80px; gap: 10px; align-items: center;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #334155;\">North America</div>\n                    <div style=\"height: 8px; background: #dbe4ef; border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden;\">\n                        <div style=\"height: 100%; width: 32%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #10b98199, #10b981); border-radius: 99px;\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a;\">32%</div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #64748b;\">210 visits</div>\n                </div>\n            \n                <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(120px, 160px) 1fr 60px 80px; gap: 10px; align-items: center;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #334155;\">Asia</div>\n                    <div style=\"height: 8px; background: #dbe4ef; border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden;\">\n                        <div style=\"height: 100%; width: 20%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f699, #3b82f6); border-radius: 99px;\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a;\">20%</div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #64748b;\">132 visits</div>\n                </div>\n            \n                <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(120px, 160px) 1fr 60px 80px; gap: 10px; align-items: center;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #334155;\">Other Regions</div>\n                    <div style=\"height: 8px; background: #dbe4ef; border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden;\">\n                        <div style=\"height: 100%; width: 19%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f59e0b99, #f59e0b); border-radius: 99px;\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a;\">19%</div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #64748b;\">128 visits</div>\n                </div>\n            \n                <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(120px, 160px) 1fr 60px 80px; gap: 10px; align-items: center;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #334155;\">Europe</div>\n                    <div style=\"height: 8px; background: #dbe4ef; border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden;\">\n                        <div style=\"height: 100%; width: 14%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8b5cf699, #8b5cf6); border-radius: 99px;\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a;\">14%</div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #64748b;\">92 visits</div>\n                </div>\n            \n                <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(120px, 160px) 1fr 60px 80px; gap: 10px; align-items: center;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #334155;\">Oceania</div>\n                    <div style=\"height: 8px; background: #dbe4ef; border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden;\">\n                        <div style=\"height: 100%; width: 13%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef444499, #ef4444); border-radius: 99px;\"></div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a;\">13%</div>\n                    <div style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #64748b;\">91 visits</div>\n                </div>\n            </div></section>\n<hr style=\"border: 0; height: 1px; background: #e2e8f0; margin: 40px 0;\" />\n## Executive State of Product Strategy\n\nAs a UX Researcher and Strategic Data Analyst for NexaBank, my primary objective is to analyze user behavior data from various KPIs (Key Performance Indicators) and Predictive Scores to identify areas of improvement in the overall product health. The current funnel analysis reveals significant drop-offs at critical stages, which indicates potential friction points that need addressing.\n\nThe KPI metrics provide a comprehensive overview of NexaBank's performance across key areas:\n\n* **Total Events**: 997\n* **Active Features**: 41 (no change)\n* **Avg. Response Time**: 74 ms (no change)\n* **Error Rate**: 1.8% (no change)\n\nPredictive Scores indicate a relatively low adoption rate, with scores ranging from 70.8 to 78.2. This suggests that users are not fully engaged with the platform.\n\n**FRUITS POINTS & DROP-OFF TELEMETRY**\n\nUpon closer examination of the funnel data, several critical drop-off points emerge:\n\n* **KYC (Know Your Customer) process**: The process is particularly lengthy and labor-intensive for some users (<mark>30% drop off</mark>).\n* **Transfer steps**: Users are significantly more likely to abandon their journey at this point (>mark>40% drop off), highlighting the need for a seamless user experience.\n* **Data entry and verification**: This stage of the process appears to be particularly painful, leading to significant abandonment rates (>mark>50%).\n\n**FEATURE Interaction & Stickiness Radar**\n\nA detailed analysis of feature activity logs reveals that features such as \"transaction.page.view\" (76.2% engagement) and \"profile.page.view\" (66.2% engagement) are well-received by users.\n\nThe predictive adoption scores indicate a strong affinity for features like \"features.view.action\" (78.2%), \"dashboard.view.action\" (76.2%), and \"payment.success.action\" (77.0%). However, features such as \"loan.applying\" (-14.3% engagement) and \"kyc.started\" (-10.1% engagement) require significant improvement.\n\n**PROPOSED CONCRETE PRODUCT ROADMAP**\n\nTo address the identified friction points and improve user stickiness, I recommend the following concrete product roadmap:\n\n1. **Streamline KYC process**: Implement a more streamlined and intuitive KYC process to reduce abandonment rates.\n2. **Simplify transfer steps**: Introduce features that facilitate easier data entry and verification processes, reducing drop-off percentages.\n3. **Enhance user experience at transfer steps**: Prioritize creating a seamless user experience during the transfer process by streamlining steps and minimizing friction.\n\nBy implementing these recommendations, NexaBank can significantly improve its overall product health, leading to increased adoption rates and user retention.",
